<div id="content" class="content wikipage" lang="en" dir="ltr">
<p id="l1">
In publishing (or other freelance or creative endeavor), monies paid to an author or other content provider based on some percentage of the revenue earned by the publisher from sale of the publication to which the author has contributed. The amount actually paid to the author is the author's share of the revenue less any <a title="Advance On Royalties" href="Advance_On_Royalties">advance on royalties</a>. 
</p>
